    RequestAdapter<T>

    StatManager
    This class is responsible for habit statistic
    StatView
    Passed start date of habit and calculates all scheduled days in between start date and end date compares to habit events, if habit event exists for that date put it in completed array if no habit event found for it put it in missed pie chart vals are completed/(completed + missed) and missed/(completed+missed)
    User
    Represents a user, and includes the usernames of all users associated with this user.
    UserManager
    This a singleton responsible for loading, saving, creating, and holding the current user's User object.
    UserTest
    Unit Test for User
    ViewHabitAdapter
    Adaptor for habit
    viewManageHabits
    This is All Habit's fragment, able to view a list of habits of user, create a new habit, edit habit when clicked on the habit
    viewMyHistory
    This is My history fragment, able to view history events, search for events and open mapsActivity to show event locations
    viewTodayFragment
    This is Today's habit fragment , can view a list of habits that are due today, and able to create habit event when clicked on habit
